Kerala weather warning dashboard

Column

Day 1

# Plot Day 1


ggplot(map_latest) +
  geom_sf(aes(fill = !!col2)) +
  scale_fill_manual(
    labels = c(
      "No alert",
      "Green alert",
      "Yello alert",
      "Orange alert",
      "Red alert",
      "Extreme heavy rainfall"
    ),
    values = c('White', 'Green', 'Yellow', 'Orange', 'Red', '#8B0000')
  ) +
  labs(title = "Kerala & Lakshadweep weather warning",
       subtitle = glue("Date: {col2} {year(now())}"),
      caption = "Source: IMD, Created by: Open-oven") +
  theme_gray()
